lenders.name: Brett
lenders.loan_because:
Typically on Kiva I look for groups of borrowers, predominately female, that sell staple items such as food, clothing, and health-related products.  I also look for a track record of past success.  

On Kiva Zip, I look for good social causes for U.S.-based entrepreneurs with a unique, sustainable business model.  In Kenya, I look for proven businesses with a clear path for growth using the Zip financing.

lenders.name: Chris & Nicole
lenders.loan_because: We are targeting hard-working people with good ideas who need capital to help lift themselves out of poverty.  We are especially interested in helping those who live in countries with little to no social welfare programs.
